title: Exceptional Contemporary Apartment Home!
posting_body: ['Call or text Spirit Real Estate Group at', 'show contact info', 'and refer to F-PS-1 for more information today!', 'Located in the rapidly growing city of Frisco, just 20 minutes north of Dallas, this property offers the ideal combination of brand new luxury apartment homes, a superior amenities package and a convenient location.', 'In addition to six million square feet of shopping within a two-mile radius, the ground floor of this complex comprises 30,000 square feet of retail and restaurants.', 'Plus, the beautiful and serene Central Park, with its artistic representations of the historic Shawnee Trail, is located right across the street.', "And if you have pets, don't worry - this a pet friendly community.", 'Spirit Real Estate Group', 'show contact info', '//  Refer to F-PS-1', '<URL>', 'Facebook: Dallas Upscale Apartment Locators', 'Not all units have the same features or amenities pictured.', ' Availability, pricing, and specials are subject to change daily depending on market conditions.', 'Pricing or specials in the ads are not always updated accordingly.', '*Frisco*', 'We service Downtown Dallas, Uptown Dallas, Richardson, Highland Village, Old East Dallas, East Dallas, Frisco, Plano, McKinney, Allen, North Dallas, Carrollton, Farmers Branch, Lewisville, Grapevine, Las Colinas, and all of the DFW Metroplex.', '**Ask us how to receive a cash rebate**']
